      <title>刚果总统选举的四大竞争者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/the-four-top-contenders-in-congo-s-presidential-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国的选民周三有 26 名总统候选人可供选择，这个矿产资源丰富的国家在经历了数十年的独裁和战争后连续第四次举行选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/the-four-top-contenders-in-congo-s-presidential-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 09:06:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿拉伯分裂阻碍美国反击胡塞武装船只袭击的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/red-sea-shipping-attacks-divisions-hinder-us-efforts-to-counter-yemen-houthis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由于华盛顿的阿拉伯盟友之间存在分歧，美国打击也门胡塞叛军的努力遇到了重大障碍，因为也门胡塞叛军袭击了世界上最重要水道之一的船只。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/red-sea-shipping-attacks-divisions-hinder-us-efforts-to-counter-yemen-houthis</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 09:00:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度反对派在现金紧缩的迹象下为选举进行众筹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/india-opposition-crowdfunds-for-election-in-sign-of-cash-squeeze</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度主要反对党周一启动了一项公共筹资活动，以对抗总理纳伦德拉·莫迪(Narendra Modi)领导的执政党的选举主宰，这表明竞争对手之间存在巨大的财政差距。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/india-opposition-crowdfunds-for-election-in-sign-of-cash-squeeze</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 08:41:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿曼寻求避免金融灰名单，重点关注伊朗关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/oman-seeks-to-avoid-financial-gray-list-with-iran-ties-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿曼是一个以其中立性以及与美国和伊朗关系密切而闻名的海湾国家，正在准备接受全球监管机构对脏钱的重要审查——希望避免邻国阿拉伯联合酋长国的命运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/oman-seeks-to-avoid-financial-gray-list-with-iran-ties-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 08:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国将从 2027 年起对钢铁进口征收气候税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/uk-to-introduce-carbon-border-tax-from-2027-after-move-by-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继欧盟采取类似举措后，英国将从 2027 年起对来自气候制度较弱国家的进口排放密集型商品征收碳边境税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/uk-to-introduce-carbon-border-tax-from-2027-after-move-by-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 07:55:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗加油站可能遭到黑客攻击，局势紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/iran-fuel-stations-disrupted-by-possible-sabotage-tv-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据石油部沙纳通讯社报道，“敌人阴谋”造成的技术问题中断了伊朗多个省份加油站的燃料供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/iran-fuel-stations-disrupted-by-possible-sabotage-tv-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 07:51:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平赞扬李光耀带领香港“拨乱反正”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/hong-kong-leader-set-to-meet-china-s-xi-in-beijing-scmp-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平赞扬香港领导人李家超维护国家安全、重塑区议会制度以及引领疫情后经济复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/hong-kong-leader-set-to-meet-china-s-xi-in-beijing-scmp-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 05:42:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>近 10,000 起性犯罪案件在英国破碎的法院系统中陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2023-12-18/does-the-uk-criminal-justice-system-still-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从人满为患的监狱到创纪录的法院积压案件，刑事司法系统正被推向崩溃边缘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2023-12-18/does-the-uk-criminal-justice-system-still-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 05:01:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚领导人的政党赢得快速投票，扩大统治地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/serbia-s-strongman-oversees-another-election-win-for-his-populist-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚总统亚历山大·武契奇的政党在周日的提前选举中取得了巨大胜利，巩固了这位巴尔干领导人在该国长达十年的统治地位，同时该国在走向欧盟的道路上摇摇欲坠。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/serbia-s-strongman-oversees-another-election-win-for-his-populist-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 20:52:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港第一保安目标黎智英出庭受审</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/hong-kong-activist-jimmy-lai-faces-security-trial-after-china-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在入狱 1000 多天后，香港镇压异见的最大目标黎智英于周一开始受审，该案受到西方政府的密切关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/hong-kong-activist-jimmy-lai-faces-security-trial-after-china-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 09:00:24 GMT</pubDate>
